        "creation_date": 1327377168,
        "body": "<p>Yes. It is cacerts. You need to use keytool import command. Keystore option should have path to your cacert location. Here is example on keytool command <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/security/toolfilex/rstep1.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/security/toolfilex/rstep1.html<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>Cacerts will be under java_home-jre-lib-security folder.<\/p>\n",
